String.string: Destroy those plans any way you can. Talk to Tulutulu to descend into Azarel's Labyrinth.
Talk to {@linkcreature:209#2000$$Tulutulu} to gain entrance to Azarel's Labyrinth Depths.
"I can't believe I ate the whole plan."
Find the centurion at the Advance Camp in Azarel's Labyrinth Depths and destroy the battle plans he carries.
